strings.Value: "What a party we have here! We somehow suit these lands. In a civilized place we'd probably all feud with each other all the time, but here the constant danger keeps us united."
"It's sad that danger and trouble are often the only things that keep us together. Even those who sincerely love each other can sometimes find they're too different to live together in peace."
